languages.text: "Мы стоим на краю обрыва, элантах. Позади — страхи и сомнения. Впереди — лишь тьма и борьба. Я готова ступить в неизвестность, дабы окончить свой путь... И начать следующий".
"We are standing on the edge of a cliff, elantach. Darkness and struggle lie ahead of us, fear and doubts lie behind. I am ready to step into the unknown to end my journey and begin the next."

languages.text: “我们此刻正站在悬崖边上，外界人。面前的道路充满了黑暗与痛苦，身后的道路遍布恐惧与怀疑。我已经准备好踏入未知之地，结束这场冒险，开始新的旅程。”
languages.original_text: "We are standing on the edge of a cliff, elantach. Darkness and struggle lie ahead of us, fear and doubts lie behind. I am ready to step into the unknown to end my journey and begin the next."

languages.text: «Nos encontramos al borde del precipicio, elantach. La oscuridad y la lucha nos aguardan más adelante, y el miedo y las dudas yacen a nuestras espaldas. Estoy lista para avanzar hacia lo desconocido. Para poner fin a mi viaje y dar comienzo a uno nuevo».
languages.original_text: "We are standing on the edge of a cliff, elantach. Darkness and struggle lie ahead of us, fear and doubts lie behind. I am ready to step into the unknown to end my journey and begin the next."

languages.text: 「星外人よ、私たちは崖っぷちに立たされているのだ。前方には暗闇と苦難が広がり、後方には恐怖と疑惑が迫っている。私には、未知の世界に足を踏み入れ、自分の旅を終わらせ、次の旅を始める準備ができている」
languages.original_text: "We are standing on the edge of a cliff, elantach. Darkness and struggle lie ahead of us, fear and doubts lie behind. I am ready to step into the unknown to end my journey and begin the next."

languages.text: "Wir stehen am Rand einer Klippe, Elantach. Dunkelheit und Mühen liegen vor uns, Angst und Zweifel liegen hinter uns. Ich bin bereit, in das Unbekannte zu treten, um meine Reise zu beenden und die nächste zu beginnen."
languages.original_text: "We are standing on the edge of a cliff, elantach. Darkness and struggle lie ahead of us, fear and doubts lie behind. I am ready to step into the unknown to end my journey and begin the next."

languages.text: « Nous nous tenons au bord d'un précipice, elantach. Il nous faut laisser derrière nous nos peurs et nos doutes alors que nous braverons les ténèbres et les combats à venir. Je suis prête à m'aventurer dans l'inconnu pour achever ce voyage et entamer le suivant. »

languages.text: "Bir uçurumun kenarında dikiliyoruz elantach. Önümüz karanlık ve zorluk, arkamız korku ve şüphe. Bilinmeyene adım atmaya, yolculuğumu sonlandırmaya ve bir sonraki yolculuğuma başlamaya hazırım."
